The failure is because your test never calls the method under test.

You stub these calls:

```java
when(pingUserMapper.toPingUser(user)).thenReturn(request);
when(pingApi.partnersBEAP74737Post(request, null, null))
        .thenReturn(response);
```

Then immediately verify them:

```java
verify(pingUserMapper).toPingUser(user);
verify(pingApi).partnersBEAP74737Post(request, null, null);
```

But `pingUserClient.createUser(user)` is missing, so Mockito correctly reports:

```text
Wanted but not invoked:
pingUserMapper.toPingUser(...)
Actually, there were zero interactions with this mock.
```

Update the test:

```java
